Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.98,0:02:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakera: A Piece Of Our Life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I've got to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:04:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm seeing her today.\NSo let's talk tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Haru.\NFirst period is cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.34,0:06:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that cocoa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Taste good?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. My name is Riko Sakata.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You had a cocoa moustache.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...\NSorry, I'm kind of sloppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why "sorry"?\NCan I sit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.30,0:07:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,An iced cocoa with no ice,\Nand a slice of cheesecake, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.78,0:07:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it a big slice, if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like cheesecake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Baked ones are better, right?\NThey're dense and rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the unbaked ones too.\NThey're fluffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your order.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That really is big.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is surprisingly good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that look on your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you do this\Nkind of thing often?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk to strangers, like you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. I'm perspiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I'm not recruiting for a cult.\NI'm not religious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor am I a sex industry recruiter,\NI have a respectable job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.22,0:09:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you are cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.34,0:10:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't always do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I just find you attractive\Nso I came over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If I let this moment pass,\NI'd never see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you ever felt that way\Nabout someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, I have.\N- Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't waste such a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.30,0:10:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I said hello and now we're talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you only interested in girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I like how girls feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I love to touch and\NI love being touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.22,0:10:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls feel soft and smell nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about if\Nyou're a man or a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have someone\Nwho you think feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"To Haru"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.42,0:13:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Call me any time.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to call before\Nyou come over, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We should stop seeing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.06,0:15:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.50,0:15:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you have hair on your upper lip!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to go to work.\NWant to walk with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Minoru's ear coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your heart into it.\NYour work is unsteady.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,0:17:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to learn to sculpt\Nwith your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.58,0:17:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God, I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you did?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sorry, I must go.\N- She'll be right with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, Ms. Yamashiro is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.10,0:18:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My lunch break is at 12:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Call from the cafe where we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.26,0:18:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's close to where I work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,See you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Sakata, your prosthetist.\NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.26,0:18:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.\NI'm Tohko Yamashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll begin with a consultation.\NFollow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Tanaka Prosthetics"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can pick them up\Nif you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the ones I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.42,0:20:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one's unique...that's pretty\Nobvious, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so impressed that\Nyou made these...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.06,0:20:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's so light.\N- It's a new material.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As airy as a balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Trythisone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.30,0:20:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's lighter than the real thing.\NNo wonder boobs cause back pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.02,0:20:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm lucky I don't have back pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.\NI never expected you to contact me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.46,0:20:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you thought I was crazy insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't\Nbut it was kind of shocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.58,0:21:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like I wanted to\Nspeak with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?\NThat's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, what do you do about\Nunwanted facial hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I leave it to grow.\NShaving stings so I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.02,0:21:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This way I can still get a\Nmilk moustache.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.22,0:21:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.38,0:21:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:22:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You smell like an animal...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.82,0:22:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know how you usually smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.38,0:22:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,0:22:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I got some.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.06,0:22:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your knickers in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.42,0:22:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.10,0:23:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.02,0:23:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a date now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.26,0:23:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.90,0:23:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But...how about your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.82,0:23:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem, I'm done for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.50,0:23:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's greatest animal...\NIt's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.70,0:23:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it is! I want to ride one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.34,0:23:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And then go around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.18,0:23:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.66,0:24:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Elephant tusks never stop growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.86,0:24:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I could be a dental prosthetist\Nand make elephant crowns.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.14,0:24:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd become world famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.14,0:24:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The Americans would put you\Nin the Guinness World Records.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.42,0:24:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And in India they'd make a\Nstatue of you. How cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.46,0:24:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't those records British?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.38,0:25:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the goat hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.62,0:25:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lucky.\NI'd love to wear a skirt like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.10,0:25:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Skirts are so easy.\NYou'd look great in one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.94,0:25:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wear skirts...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.86,0:25:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't suit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.02,0:25:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly, you'd look great\Nin one, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.22,0:25:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- You'd look great!\N- No, I wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.58,0:25:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.58,0:25:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- No!\N- Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.34,0:26:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.26,0:26:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, goat-hair girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.66,0:26:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Goats are my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.30,0:26:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.70,0:26:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to marry one?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.78,0:26:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Marry a goat?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.66,0:26:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.38,0:26:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Sakata Dry-cleaners"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.30,0:26:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.38,0:26:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.34,0:26:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.30,0:27:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.66,0:27:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hello, sir.\N- Hi there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.26,0:27:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Dad, where's Mum?\N- She's inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.82,0:27:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She's eating with us tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.70,0:27:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Haru Kitagawa.\NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.10,0:27:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise. I'm Riko's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.18,0:27:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She knows that already, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.26,0:27:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.70,0:27:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.\NRound the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.58,0:27:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.14,0:27:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.74,0:27:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mum.\N- Riko, don't shout.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.18,0:27:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.46,0:27:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a friend.\NShe's eating here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.86,0:27:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.34,0:27:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be formal.\NCome upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.14,0:27:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Your parents seem nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.30,0:28:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They are.\NThere's one more of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.10,0:28:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.34,0:28:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.18,0:28:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and sit down, Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.26,0:28:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This seems kind of strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.46,0:28:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.34,0:28:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really, really\Nlike girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.86,0:28:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I like girls.\NIt's you I like, Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.10,0:28:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells nice in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.14,0:29:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Men and women are all humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.90,0:29:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only hard when we\Ncategorise ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.58,0:29:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Homo sapiens have 23 pairs of\Nnuclear chromosomes per cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.26,0:29:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Among those pairs,there are\Nsex chromosomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.62,0:29:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,XX makes a female and\NXY makes a male.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.50,0:29:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So it comes down to this,\N"Do you have a Y chromosome?"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.38,0:29:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Answering "No" will determine if\Nyou are a man or a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.02,0:29:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Women have a {\i1}field{\i}\Nwhere the crop grows.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.78,0:29:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a crop field of\NX chromosomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.70,0:29:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In this field a seed is sowed called\Nsperm, with X and Y chromosomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.82,0:30:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,As the seed copulates with the field,\Nconception occurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.02,0:30:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This may suggest that
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.06,0:30:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the difference between a man and\Na woman depends on the sperm.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.78,0:30:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I doubt that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.14,0:30:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we don't need to define\Nourselves as man or woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.58,0:30:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's as arbitrary as whether\Nthe zoo was open or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.26,0:30:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What we do know is that\Nin the beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.46,0:30:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,all humans start out being women.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.74,0:31:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.14,0:31:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you two are very comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.66,0:31:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.10,0:31:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.78,0:31:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the one I mentioned before.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.18,0:31:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll forget soon.\NShe's a bit senile.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.34,0:31:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A kiss for our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.42,0:31:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.78,0:32:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A kiss for our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.02,0:32:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I'm going to ditch her. Ryota"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.98,0:32:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tin Drum, or\N{\i1}Die Blechtrommel.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.90,0:32:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The motif of\NOskar Matzerath, the protagonist
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.30,0:32:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is clearly alluded to {\i1}in Frau Holle{\i}\Nfrom the Brothers Grimm tales.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.34,0:33:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In {\i1}Frau{\i} Holle, there's\Na daughter and a stepdaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.98,0:33:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The apples symbolise life and\Nthe oven symbolises burning hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.06,0:33:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And the bottom of the well symbolises\Nthe uterus of the daughters.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.62,0:33:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,These three elements represent\Nthe ancient Germanic psyche and
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.82,0:33:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,also represent the purgatory\Nthat girls live in now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.46,0:33:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In The Tin Drum, Oscar refuses\Nto grow older than 3
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.78,0:33:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's really 30 inside.\NHe has this duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.14,0:33:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,His dilemma is that of\Npost-war Germany
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.54,0:33:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and the dilemma is\Nembraced in women's skirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.22,0:35:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Haru?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.74,0:35:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.78,0:36:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.22,0:37:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good luck charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.38,0:37:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- For me?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.58,0:37:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always be on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.54,0:38:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.30,0:38:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They're geraniums.\NThey're my favourite.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.26,0:38:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,White ones are not so common.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.42,0:38:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The plainness of white is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.66,0:38:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.02,0:38:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.46,0:38:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.86,0:38:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'll get your forms now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.14,0:38:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, isn't this your day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.42,0:38:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's perfectly OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.42,0:39:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Takahashi was telling me his story.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.50,0:39:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How as a kid, your boss made legs\Nfor him and now he works here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.26,0:39:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's touching.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.30,0:39:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And happily married with 2 children.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.38,0:39:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.18,0:39:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe everything to those legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.10,0:39:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.70,0:39:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.78,0:39:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.78,0:39:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell me?\NI want to know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.30,0:39:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- You know...\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.74,0:39:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.74,0:39:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why I like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.38,0:39:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. You don't plan love.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.66,0:39:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like I just fell in a huge hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.98,0:40:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And a twine came flying at me,\Ngrabbing my heart really tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.26,0:40:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart started to thump\Nlike crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.06,0:40:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.94,0:40:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.62,0:40:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.62,0:40:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's watch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.38,0:40:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They're far away... but beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.42,0:40:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Winter fireworks...\NSee how the smoke lingers?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.70,0:40:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Fireworks look like they are\Nshooting up but
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.66,0:40:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,they also look like they're falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.14,0:40:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this is what war is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.26,0:40:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.98,0:40:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you choose your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.18,0:41:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help\Npeople with something missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.66,0:41:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My family business is to clean\Nwhat's dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.02,0:41:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in our blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.34,0:41:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the moon is full\Nonly once a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.30,0:41:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Every other day, it's fragmented.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.42,0:41:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But the crescent moon's also beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.26,0:41:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do, Haru?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.98,0:41:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.18,0:41:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be... loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.14,0:42:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember you said that you liked to\Nfeel girls because they were softer?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.98,0:42:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought something similar once.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.54,0:42:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I was put under anaesthesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.34,0:42:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Years ago, I had a pain so severe\NI couldn't even walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.34,0:42:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctors gave me injections the size\Nof ice-picks everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.58,0:42:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.66,0:42:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The injections made me numb from\Nmy waist down.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.82,0:42:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So I tried to grab my butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.26,0:42:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt like I was feeling somebody\Nelse's butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.30,0:42:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My hands had full sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.10,0:42:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But my butt was senseless.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.66,0:43:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when I thought to myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.58,0:43:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"How lucky men are to touch something\Nso soft and cuddly..."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.02,0:43:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't a kiss for\Nour friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.70,0:44:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.82,0:44:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only here so we can talk\Nabout this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.06,0:44:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And as I said, you were wrong\Nabout the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.78,0:44:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We broke up but then she came over.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.46,0:44:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.90,0:44:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not! Why would I lie to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.10,0:44:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I realise now that I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.06,0:44:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.30,0:44:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I really broke up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.94,0:44:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just turn someone away\Nwhen they visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.62,0:44:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.74,0:44:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But you guys were\Nwalking together...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.74,0:44:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.90,0:45:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.70,0:45:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru, your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.82,0:45:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.98,0:46:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hi, this is Riko.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.82,0:46:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, are you Haru's friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.42,0:46:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.58,0:46:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, it's your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.14,0:46:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.14,0:46:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She hung up.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.18,0:47:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw him again?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.70,0:47:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.02,0:47:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you stay over?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.90,0:47:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You slept with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.10,0:47:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where to start...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.94,0:47:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.54,0:47:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ever escape him?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.66,0:47:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.22,0:47:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear this bullshit.\NYou're just being indecisive!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.62,0:47:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- No.\N- You fucked him!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.26,0:47:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.62,0:47:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you help me through this?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.54,0:47:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You know your problem, you're weak!\NYou make me sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.66,0:47:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't understand me because we\Nhave different taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.42,0:47:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that I can't understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.62,0:47:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't fall in love {\i1}for taste.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.06,0:48:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru, you're not in love with\Nyour boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.02,0:48:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You deceive yourself by feigning\Nacceptance in the name of love...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.50,0:48:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you can be with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.38,0:48:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't leave the relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.54,0:48:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's simpler for you to\Nindulge in your own weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.98,0:48:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just easy for him\Nto have around.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.86,0:48:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never loved a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.18,0:48:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me what's wrong\Nwith my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.74,0:48:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You look innocent but you're mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.78,0:48:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I might not know about men
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.18,0:48:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've known many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.10,0:48:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You just want sex, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.46,0:48:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.30,0:48:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Some things you can't say\Neven to your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.74,0:49:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me what I'm like!\NYou don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.98,0:49:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not finished yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.90,0:49:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.66,0:49:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.54,0:49:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.90,0:49:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.26,0:49:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you understand that I've\Nnever thought of you as a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.62,0:49:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.10,0:49:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've wanted to be someone\Nspecial to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.82,0:49:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We spend so much time together\Nbut you don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.74,0:49:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you in my arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.18,0:49:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hold you and kiss you\Na million times!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.74,0:51:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.50,0:51:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up? You look like you're\Nat a funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.78,0:51:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just preoccupied...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.50,0:51:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.54,0:51:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.34,0:51:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But she has a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.02,0:51:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.86,0:51:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody rescue me...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.86,0:51:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my hubby.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.38,0:51:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.86,0:52:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's like roses.\NIt's good because it has thorns.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.38,0:52:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Women's weapon is our crotch.\NSo use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.26,0:52:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Drink up and\Npull yourself together.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.22,0:53:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Yamashiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.38,0:53:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, I'm Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.46,0:53:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.14,0:53:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your prosthetist.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.90,0:53:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.66,0:53:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Riko Sakata.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.14,0:53:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember me!\NYou're Ms. Yamashiro, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.98,0:53:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You are all in black and antsy...\NLike an {\i1}ant... an ari.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.86,0:53:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Muhammad?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.22,0:53:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Muhammad {\i1}Ali.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.10,0:53:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you are also a mean fighter\Nlike him. Right, Muhammad?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.22,0:54:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.58,0:54:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know him? Fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.62,0:54:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.94,0:54:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty, Muhammad.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.14,0:54:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.94,0:54:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me Tohko.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.22,0:54:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.94,0:54:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?\NYou usually play along.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.06,0:55:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.78,0:55:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.94,0:55:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.14,0:55:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you mad at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.06,0:55:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you stink!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.62,0:55:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.18,0:55:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.26,0:55:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We meet, have sex...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.10,0:55:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We meet to have sex!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.42,0:55:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.70,0:55:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's indecent.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.14,0:55:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.82,0:55:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's love to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.50,0:55:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a girlfriend to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.34,0:56:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be bothered.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.70,0:56:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I know you?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.98,0:56:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so self-centred.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.82,0:56:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is ever going to\Nget better.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.98,0:56:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it, good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.86,0:57:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finished...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.06,0:57:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.42,0:57:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.38,1:01:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka Prosthetics.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.62,1:01:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.94,1:01:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.82,1:01:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run, you're making\Nthe dust fly!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.46,1:01:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.14,1:01:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- Who is it?\N- Ms. Yamashiro.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.70,1:01:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When you concentrate\Nyou don't hear a thing!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.50,1:01:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Sakata speaking.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.78,1:01:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Muhammad, get snappy!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.78,1:01:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What time will you finish?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.94,1:01:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick me up now.\NHave coffee with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.38,1:01:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.66,1:01:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.90,1:02:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.06,1:02:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to deliver something.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.70,1:02:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to run now, Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.58,1:02:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- See you later.\N- Take care.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.02,1:02:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop bugging me...\NI'm leaving now!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.26,1:02:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Haru"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.58,1:02:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.18,1:02:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, it's been a while.\NSorry, I know you're working.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.38,1:03:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you talk now?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.18,1:03:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.06,1:03:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think I want to see you.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.58,1:03:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, let's meet.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.26,1:03:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late!\NI was just about to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.58,1:03:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry. I can explain.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.78,1:03:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.54,1:03:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to but I can't today.\NI have to meet my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.02,1:03:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.62,1:03:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We drifted apart after a fight but\Nshe called me just now.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.14,1:04:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to patch things up.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.58,1:04:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't go.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.46,1:04:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.78,1:04:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You know perfectly well that you'll\Nhave more fun with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.66,1:04:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohko, I've been in love\Nwith her all along.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.02,1:04:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be more than just friends\Nbut I didn't know how.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.14,1:04:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I got frustrated and was mean to her.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.18,1:04:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make it up with her.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.22,1:04:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big deal?\NIs she more important to you than me?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.22,1:04:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohko.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.98,1:04:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm putting everything I have into\Nmaking your body part.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.74,1:04:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't fulfil the hollow\Nyou have in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.10,1:05:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't be friends\Nunless you try harder.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.30,1:05:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about the other day.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.62,1:05:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.78,1:05:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been busy?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.50,1:05:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Same as usual.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.14,1:05:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty quick at what I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.18,1:05:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm making a boob.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.26,1:06:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.50,1:06:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.10,1:06:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But yummy.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.42,1:06:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"As Shirota embraced Chika, he felt{\i}\N{\i1}his chest swell.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.86,1:06:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her perspiration faintly tantalised{\i}\N{\i1}his nostrils.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.74,1:06:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Which drove him to press his{\i}\N{\i1}pelvis to hers.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.94,1:06:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As if to wipe off the bloodshed last{\i}\N{\i1}night, Chika wiggled her tongue{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.06,1:06:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and lapped at his nape, like a{\i}\N{\i1}wild beast would.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.14,1:06:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stripped now down to{\i}\N{\i1}manhood and womanhood,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.58,1:06:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}they fucked the shit out of{\i}\N{\i1}each other."{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.66,1:06:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that story?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.22,1:06:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.78,1:07:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's going on with my hair?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.34,1:07:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.38,1:07:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand those stories.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.78,1:07:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again, we're the result of\Nmale/female copulation.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.18,1:07:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Both you and I.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.38,1:07:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum and Dad did it in a house,\Nscented with softener.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.06,1:07:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result I came\Nout of that tiny cavity.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.38,1:07:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds so wicked.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.82,1:07:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it isn't. It's wonderful really.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.82,1:07:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like those mushroom heads.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.62,1:07:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Except Dad's thing.\NIt's a love tool.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.10,1:07:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In the future I shall live my life\Nclose to Virgin Mary.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.18,1:08:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haru.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.94,1:08:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haru.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.22,1:08:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.50,1:08:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The owner of the erotic novel.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.66,1:08:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haru, open up.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.22,1:08:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is major! I have huge news.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.14,1:08:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of busy now.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.70,1:08:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The professor made me an assistant\Non account of my thesis.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.06,1:08:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So I kissed my job good-bye!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.22,1:08:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Your line was busy so I came over.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.74,1:08:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you, Haru?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.74,1:08:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I found someone.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.02,1:08:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You must be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.62,1:08:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we really enjoy each other's\Ncompany.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.78,1:08:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, thanks for taking care of Haru.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.58,1:08:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.74,1:08:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she a school friend?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.26,1:09:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Riko.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.78,1:09:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Riko, Haru's new love.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.66,1:09:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.62,1:09:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, now excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.26,1:09:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.94,1:09:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in love with this woman?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.02,1:09:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is she a dyke?\N{\i1}- Is she a dyke?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.62,1:09:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going with a woman now, Haru?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.10,1:09:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm confused.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.98,1:09:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been sleeping with\Na lesbian?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.14,1:09:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's gross.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.18,1:09:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave! Go away now!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.82,1:09:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to do with us! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.58,1:09:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Balls don't make you superior!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.50,1:09:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe one day you'll adapt to the\Nglobal modern world.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.42,1:09:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Asshole.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.46,1:10:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you asleep?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.42,1:10:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.90,1:11:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I might be late tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.02,1:11:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It could take me all night.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.58,1:11:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a precious finger to finish.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.14,1:12:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.14,1:12:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Droopy eyes, sleepy eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.02,1:12:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.90,1:12:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My client was determined\Nto have a church wedding
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.62,1:12:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and exchange rings with the groom.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.58,1:12:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm making her ring finger\Nwith my blessings.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.38,1:13:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you got?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.34,1:13:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.70,1:13:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so hungry! Let's eat them.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.58,1:13:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.62,1:13:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, you bought too many things.\NWhat will you cook?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.54,1:13:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I could make curry I guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.66,1:13:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give it some thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.50,1:13:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm. Can I have the fizzy drink?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.42,1:13:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second then...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.46,1:13:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, princess.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.10,1:13:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't throw the drink!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.06,1:14:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, catch!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.26,1:14:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.46,1:14:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.78,1:14:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been?\NWe thought you'd vanished.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.86,1:14:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been coming to school, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.82,1:14:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Only last week.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.70,1:14:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get the party invite?\NYou're coming, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.14,1:14:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... I guess somebody texted me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.66,1:14:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to come.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.10,1:14:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir, reporting for duty.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.78,1:15:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. I was worried about you\Nbecause we haven't seen you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.66,1:15:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Make time for us, will you?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.22,1:15:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I will, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.46,1:15:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.78,1:15:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime why don't you\Ncome with us now?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.62,1:15:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.02,1:15:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Tetsu.\NHe's a freshman and pretty fun too.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.66,1:15:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Haru. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.62,1:15:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tetsu, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.94,1:15:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.26,1:16:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.06,1:16:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.10,1:16:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.02,1:16:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The bride couldn't be happier with\Nyour work. Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.98,1:16:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She sends her regards to you, Riko.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.10,1:16:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.62,1:16:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm the happiest man on earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.86,1:16:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, white undies.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.46,1:17:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru, why don't we plan something\Nfor next week.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.10,1:17:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We can go away, just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.54,1:17:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to go to a\Nuniversity party.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.26,1:17:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.14,1:17:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.50,1:17:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a date tomorrow then?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.70,1:17:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pick the place.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.14,1:17:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.86,1:17:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a sentence I want to\Nhear you say.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.14,1:17:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It starts with "I" and\Nends with "U".
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.70,1:17:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How about...\N"I want to eat Chicken Cordon Bleu."
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.86,1:17:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so wrong...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.10,1:17:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, literature major.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.74,1:18:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.26,1:18:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's "I'll bring ice cream\Nto you."
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.70,1:18:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring you some.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.58,1:18:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You come here often?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.90,1:18:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first time.\NI'm with my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.94,1:18:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I really love this band.\NHave you seen them play before?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.98,1:18:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.78,1:19:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think you're talking to?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.62,1:19:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the friend?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.78,1:19:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.30,1:19:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- You like the band too?\N- Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.98,1:19:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.86,1:19:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.06,1:19:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We're totally, exclusively in love!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.90,1:19:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I love her more than anybody\Nin the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.34,1:19:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool. Unreal!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.42,1:20:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Haru?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.54,1:20:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I want to go...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.66,1:20:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.78,1:20:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in love with Haru!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.30,1:20:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not ready to say that aloud...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.70,1:21:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.50,1:21:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Brrrr, it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.06,1:21:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A towel...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.54,1:21:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a towel.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.18,1:21:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Busy working on an essay?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.78,1:22:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Home, sweet home. It's so warm.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.02,1:22:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Change your clothes.\NYou'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.86,1:22:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you quit university?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.66,1:22:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we can go somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.22,1:22:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.98,1:22:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not listening to me, Haru.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.78,1:22:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,About tomorrow night
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.78,1:22:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm meeting friends so\NI might be late.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.14,1:22:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.34,1:22:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Shibuya, I guess...\NDidn't I tell you before?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.78,1:22:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Really... Maybe I can come too.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.98,1:22:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're not a student.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.86,1:22:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm lonely I'll come and get you.\NLet me know where you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.94,1:22:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.70,1:23:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Jesus, her boobs are too big.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.38,1:23:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,American porn is tacky.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.38,1:23:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They're like melons.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.18,1:23:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Silicon enhanced. And a face job too.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.34,1:23:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you boys always watch\Nthis stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.90,1:23:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I live with my parents so I can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.22,1:23:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just jealous, Yumiko.\NAnything for a hard-on!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.18,1:23:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You get hard watching this?\NWhat a cheap cocktail sausage!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.42,1:23:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I watched one with animals.\NA white horse and a blond.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.18,1:23:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds interesting...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.02,1:23:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Tetsu, he's corrupting you.\NStay away from him.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.62,1:23:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat this and shut up.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.98,1:24:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, can you turn off\Nthis porn?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.78,1:24:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a remote behind you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.62,1:24:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Eri, pass me the remote!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.82,1:24:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a boyfriend, Haru?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.06,1:24:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She just broke up with one.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.46,1:24:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of men do you like?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.58,1:24:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Gorgeous guys, over 7 feet tall...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.06,1:24:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,With long, blond hair...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.50,1:24:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And muscular...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.06,1:24:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening? He has to have\Na goatee and be fashionable.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.90,1:24:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.34,1:24:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haru, what are you doing now?.{\i}\N{\i1}I'm so lonely.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.22,1:24:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I'm drinking\Nwith my friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.98,1:24:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody, come to the table!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.22,1:24:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hello?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.74,1:25:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru, help me out!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.78,1:25:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that? It's so noisy there.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.14,1:25:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. It was Tetsu,\None of the guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.50,1:25:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there men there?\NYou didn't tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.06,1:25:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course there are.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.10,1:25:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll call you later.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.62,1:25:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.38,1:25:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.46,1:25:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.02,1:25:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yumiko, do an impersonation!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.26,1:26:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I love this audience!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.58,1:26:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I look old?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.66,1:26:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, about 30 or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.14,1:26:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a big head.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.66,1:26:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that already!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.46,1:26:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.66,1:27:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Haru.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.58,1:27:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, another girl!\NThe more the merrier.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.66,1:27:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.18,1:27:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so stylish.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.70,1:27:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.\NGive me another beer.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.42,1:28:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru, are you asleep?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.58,1:28:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.30,1:28:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleep well...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.90,1:29:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru, I can finish work at noon\Nso we can go somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.62,1:29:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a movie?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.98,1:29:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why so noncommittal?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.70,1:29:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... I guess I should\Ngo back to my parents'.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.42,1:29:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You look kind of frustrated too...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.14,1:29:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we need some space.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.34,1:30:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.66,1:30:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.46,1:30:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.62,1:31:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru...?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.74,1:31:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better not to overeat\Nfood you love.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.98,1:32:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You make yourself sick.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.14,1:32:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Favourite foods are better eaten\Na little at a time.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.90,1:32:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's a beautiful day.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.26,1:33:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.42,1:33:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.10,1:34:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to answer it?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.06,1:34:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It stopped.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.22,1:34:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's OK. I know it's Haru.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.10,1:34:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cold, Muhammad.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.94,1:34:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're cool to me too. You're mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.02,1:34:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.78,1:34:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave you my body and soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.98,1:34:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Riko, Takahashi\Ngave me your body and soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.78,1:35:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I see it on you?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.18,1:35:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.66,1:36:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so soft...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.14,1:37:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hello.\N- Hi, there.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.94,1:37:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can I have a mandarin?\N- You want the mandarins.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.50,1:38:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- Just one, please.\N- Just one? It's 30 yen.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.82,1:38:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.94,1:38:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I forgot my wallet.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.82,1:38:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No money?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.22,1:38:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.90,1:38:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But you want a mandarin.\NTake it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.18,1:38:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Go ahead.\N- Is it OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.42,1:38:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.26,1:38:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.70,1:40:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Muhammad.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.58,1:40:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.74,1:40:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She's finally started to\Nget to you, hasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.14,1:40:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She hasn't called you recently.\NI guess it's over.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.38,1:41:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.38,1:41:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Find another lover?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.54,1:41:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
